      "content": "okay i hear you. i just feel like i've been having such a rough time with this tooth ache and i'm so stressed. i was thinking maybe if i just wait a few hours after my last dose it might be okay? like if the pill is already mostly out of my system would that make it safer to just have that one glass?",
